nced Run</td><td style=\"padding:20px 12px;color:#059669;font-weight:600\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\">—</td><td style=\"padding:20px 12px\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;background:#f1f5f9;color:#475569\" class=\"jsx-2b2fd5f238fe2f81\">Community Favorite</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></section><section id=\"park-collections\" class=\"park-collections-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Curated collections</span><h2>Choose the vibe that fits your next outing</h2><p>Segmented park groupings built from live data so you can jump straight to the experiences that matter most.</p></div><div class=\"park-type-guide-wrapper\"><section id=\"park-types-guide\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d park-types-guide-section\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d collection-cards-grid\"><article class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d collection-guide-card \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-header\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-header-top\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d spots-pill\">10<!-- --> spots</span><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-rating\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-star-fill\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">4.7<!-- --> avg</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-type-info\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d type-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-tree-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\"><h3 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Dog Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d short-description\">Traditional outdoor off‑leash areas and fenced runs, optimized for everyday exercise.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-content \"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What is it?</h4><p class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Traditional outdoor off-leash areas where dogs can run freely and socialize with other dogs.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Key Features</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d features-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Fenced enclosures</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Open grass areas</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Agility equipment</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Water stations</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Waste disposal</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Best For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">High-energy dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Owners looking for free exercise options</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash (for entering/exiting)</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Waste bags</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Toys</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Check park rules before visiting</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog&#x27;s vaccinations up to date</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Supervise your dog at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Clean up after your dog immediately</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other dogs and owners</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></button><a class=\"jump-link\" href=\"#dog-park-parks\">Jump to list<i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></a></div></article></div></section></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog Park</span><small>10</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Dogboken of Hoboken</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>5.0</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Furever Fresh Dog Grooming</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.9</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Trusty Tails Pet Care</p><span>Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.8</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Hoboken</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Hoboken dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Hoboken</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Hoboken</h3><p>10<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.7<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">10</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/camp-bow-wow-hoboken\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Camp Bow Wow Hoboken</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Camp Bow Wow in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is an industry-leading, all-inclusive canine destination that offers a high-standard &#x27;summer camp&#x27; experience for the modern urban dog. Located on Grand Street, this massive, state-of-the-art facility features four distinct play yards specifically designed to accommodate different dog sizes—ranging from &#x27;teacups&#x27; to large breeds—ensuring a secure and socially appropriate environment for all levels of energy. The resort&#x27;s flagship overnight boarding program features 54 spacious cabins, including three ultra-luxury suites, where guests rest on cozy cots with fleece blankets and receive signature nightly &#x27;Campfire Treats™.&#x27; Every stay is all-inclusive, meaning there are no hidden fees for medication administration or individualized requests, providing total transparency and peace of mind for pet parents.\n\nSafety and technical excellence are the cornerstones of the Camp Bow Wow experience, with a team of Certified Counselors who are extensively trained in dog behavior, pet CPR, and specialized first aid. The facility&#x27;s high-tech infrastructure includes live webcams in every play yard, allowing owners to check in on their dogs&#x27; activities from any mobile device or computer throughout the day. Beyond standard play, the resort offers an innovative &#x27;Dog Enrichment&#x27; program that stimulates natural instincts through sensory adventures and small-group activities like &#x27;Sniff &amp; Seek&#x27; and one-on-one &#x27;Snuggle Time.&#x27; The facility also maintains a professional grooming department to ensure every &#x27;camper&#x27; returns home looking and smelling exceptional. With its verified status as a premier NJ boarding facility and its commitment to provided a first day free for new members, Camp Bow Wow delivers a high-touch, authoritative care solution. Whether your dog is joining for a day of spirited social socialization or an extended luxury holiday, the team treats every guest with the expert logic and individualized affection they deserve.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/church-square-park-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Church Square Park Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Church Square Park Dog Park sits at the vibrant heart of [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj), acting as the social living room for the neighborhood&#x27;s canine residents. Flanked by historic brownstones and the lush greenery of the larger Church Square Park, this dog run is a picturesque spot for daily exercise. The facility features a high-quality artificial turf surface, a welcome feature for owners who want to avoid the dust and dirt of gravel runs. Thoughtfully divided into separate sections for small and large breeds, it allows for safe, size-appropriate play that puts nervous owners at ease.\\n\\nThe park&#x27;s central location ensures it is almost always buzzing with activity, making it the perfect place for social dogs to meet their &#x27;pack&#x27;. Benches line the perimeter, offering a comfortable place for humans to chat while keeping an eye on the action. During the summer, the mature trees of the surrounding park provide welcome shade. Its popularity means it can get crowded during peak after-work hours, often humorously referred to as &#x27;yappy hour&#x27;, but the friendly community vibe makes sharing the space a pleasure. With easy access to downtown Hoboken&#x27;s dog-friendly cafes, it’s the perfect starting point for a weekend adventure.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/dog-grooming-daycare-hoboken-playful-paws-usa\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Dog Grooming &amp; Daycare Hoboken - Playful Paws USA</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 8:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Playful Paws USA in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is a newly renovated, premier pet destination that brings a sophisticated and multi-functional approach to urban canine care. Located at 712 Jefferson Street, this bright and welcoming facility is designed to be a high-standard &#x27;one-stop shop&#x27; for the modern city dog, offering everything from state-of-the-art daycare and professional grooming to expert dog walking and personalized boarding. The daycare area is a standout feature, providing separate play zones for large and small breeds equipped with professional agility equipment and structured social activities. Every animal guest benefits from a climate-controlled environment and filtered drinking water, while their experience is overseen by a professional team of certified handlers and AKC-recognized groomers who prioritize safety and emotional well-being above all else.\n\nThe service menu at Playful Paws is exceptionally granular, featuring a signature &#x27;Puppy Package&#x27; specifically designed to desensitize young dogs to the grooming process and a full-service salon that offers everything from therapeutic deep-conditioning and medicated baths to technical deshedding and color enhancement. Owners enjoy unparalleled transparency through GPS-tracked walk check-ins and regular digital updates that include daily photos and personalized notes. For those using their boarding services, the facility even offers specialized video calls via Skype or FaceTime, allowing owners to stay connected with their companions during extended stays. Playful Paws is a fully insured, bonded, and government-registered company, reinforcing its status as a verified and authoritative local resource. With its recent world-class upgrades and a staff described as exceptionally professional and passionate, this Hoboken staple delivers a premium pet care solution. Whether your pup is joining for a day of spirited social play or a restorative grooming session, the team treats every guest with the elite logic and care they deserve.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/dogboken-of-hoboken\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Dogboken of Hoboken</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 8:30 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Dogboken of Hoboken in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is a premier canine destination that has been a trusted community staple for over a decade, offering a sophisticated and outside-focused approach to daycare, boarding, and transportation. Unlike traditional indoor facilities, Dogboken&#x27;s flagship daycare program prioritizes vigorous outdoor activity, providing guests with 5 to 6 hours of supervised playground and park time every day to ensure maximum physical enrichment. This commitment to fresh-air socialization is supported by a unique enrollment model that encourages a consistent 3-day-per-week schedule, fostering deeper social bonds between dogs and a more cohesive playgroup environment. Their facility on 10th Street serves as a secure home base for an array of services that cater to the busy urban professional and their active companions.\n\nThe service menu at Dogboken is remarkably granular, offering everything from 2-hour high-energy group play sessions to comprehensive overnight &#x27;Slumber Parties&#x27; for long-term travelers. Their boarding program provides a safe, 24/7 supervised haven where dogs are treated like family in a home-style setting that includes plenty of walks and personalized care plans. For those requiring total logistical support, the facility offers a reliable &#x27;Dog Taxi&#x27; service, providing safe pick-up and drop-off throughout Hoboken, Weehawken, and Jersey City. The staff is composed of certified animal lovers who prioritize safety through the use of professional-grade gear and scrupulous monitoring of all outdoor social activities. With sibling packages available and a perfect 5.0-star reputation, Dogboken delivers an authoritative and exceptionally energetic care solution. Whether your pup is joining for a spirited morning walk or a week-long resort stay, the team treats every guest with the elite logic and outdoor-oriented heart that defines the Hoboken lifestyle.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/furever-fresh-dog-grooming\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Furever Fresh Dog Grooming</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 9:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Furever Fresh Dog Grooming in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is a premier, open-concept boutique that brings a world-class sense of luxury and &#x27;stress-free&#x27; hygiene to the 1st Street canine community. This flagship location is celebrated for its commitment to high-standard pet wellness, featuring a cage-free design where only 2-3 dogs are groomed simultaneously to ensure every guest receives the stylist&#x27;s undivided, expert attention. The salon&#x27;s hallmark is its absolute dedication to skin health, utilizing 100% natural, organic, and non-toxic products that are specifically engineered for animals with sensitive systems. Its vibrant and modern layout is scrupulously cleaned throughout the day, providing a fresh and restorative atmosphere that is highly valued by its verified 4.9-star local following.\n\nThe service menu at Furever Fresh is exceptionally granular, offering a full suite of technical styling options from therapeutic &#x27;Full Groom&#x27; packages and precision haircuts to specialized puppy acclimation sessions. Every session includes essential high-touch hygiene services such as detailed ear cleaning, deep teeth brushing, and professional nail filing, often finished with a signature bandana as a charming aesthetic touch. For those seeking specialized care, the salon provides authoritative treatments for technical de-shedding, medicated baths for skin relief, and professional anal gland expression. To maintain total transparency and convenience, the facility offers a client-centric online booking system and a clear, all-inclusive pricing model with no hidden fees. While this location focuses exclusively on elite grooming, it serves as an essential hub for pet parents who value professional reliability and a gentle, affectionate approach to animal care. Whether your companion is in need of a refreshing basic bath or a full breed-standard transformation, the team here treats every guest with the elite logic and personalized heart that defines their professional mission.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/shipyard-park-dog-park\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Shipyard Park Dog Park</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill open\">Open</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Closes at 10:00 PM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Shipyard Park Dog Park in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is a spectacular and meticulously designed urban run that offers some of the most stunning views in Northern New Jersey, overlooking the Hudson River and the world-famous Manhattan skyline. Situated at the Shipyard Dog Run, this fully fenced, off-leash destination features a premium astro-turf play surface that provides a clean and durable environment for dogs of all sizes. The facility is intelligently divided to separate active play zones from more tranquil areas, with a specialized section designated for smaller breeds. The park&#x27;s signature double-gated entry system ensures that every pet remains secure while transitioning in and out of the run, while the open-air layout provides a refreshing river breeze that makes it a favorite spot for local owners even during the warmer months.\n\nThe amenities at Shipyard Park are comprehensive and well-maintained, featuring multiple benches for pet parents to relax and socialize, along with scrupulously monitored waste stations and consistently stocked trash receptacles. During high-temperature days, the park&#x27;s local community often provides interactive blow-up pools and hose stations to keep pups cool and hydrated, adding a unique &#x27;backyard community&#x27; feel to this high-end urban space. The park also features access to a nearby walking trail and traditional grass pier areas for those seeking a more quiet leashed experience following their off-leash play. With its verified reputation for cleanliness and its unparalleled picturesque location, Shipyard Park Dog Park delivers an authoritative and essential resource for the Hoboken community. Whether your dog is a high-energy athlete looking for a game of chase on the turf or a smaller pup seeking social proofing in a safe environment, this park treats every guest with the professional logic and natural beauty its waterfront setting provides.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/trusty-tails-pet-care\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Trusty Tails Pet Care</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Trusty Tails Pet Care in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is a distinguished, high-standard in-home care provider that specializes in providing a stress-free and restorative alternative to traditional boarding facilities. Serving the Hoboken, Jersey City, and Weehawken communities, this facility-exclusive service is celebrated for its &#x27;home-happiness&#x27; philosophy, prioritizing the psychological well-being of dogs, cats, and even rabbits by maintaining their familiar routines in their own environment. The hallmark of the Trusty Tails experience is its absolute commitment to accountability, providing pet parents with detailed daily digital journals, professional photos, and GPS-verified walk summaries after every visit. Their staff of professional, background-checked caretakers is verified for their expertise in handling diverse pet needs, including the administration of complex medications and specialized puppy routine management.\n\nThe service menu at Trusty Tails is remarkably flexible and customizable, featuring unique amenities like the signature &#x27;Almost Overnight&#x27; sitting option and professional in-home puppy care visits spaced specifically at four-hour intervals to support early development. For feline owners, the team provides specialized &#x27;Cat Happiness&#x27; visits that focus on emotional enrichment, litter hygiene, and meticulous social interaction. The company is fully insured, bonded, and backed by a neighborhood-based backup team, ensuring that every pet is covered even in the event of unforeseen scheduling changes. Owners manage their companions&#x27; care through a sophisticated online portal that handles everything from recurring billing to last-minute session requests with professional ease. With a status as an authoritative and deeply affectionate local resource, Trusty Tails Pet Care delivers an elite solution for those seeking the highest level of individualized attention. Whether your companion is a senior dog in need of a quiet walk or a multi-pet household requiring overnight supervision, the team here treats every guest with the expert logic and personalized heart they would their own family.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/urban-dog-fuzzybutz-dog-grooming-dog-walking-daycare-and-boarding\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Urban Dog / Fuzzybutz Dog Grooming, Dog Walking, Daycare and Boarding</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Hoboken<!-- -->, <!-- -->NJ</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Urban Dog / Fuzzybutz Dog Grooming and Daycare in [Hoboken](/cities/hoboken-nj) is an elite pet care destination that combines high-fashion aesthetic grooming with a revolutionary, home-style approach to social play. Operating out of the world-class facility at 60 Madison Street, this destination is particularly famous for its signature &#x27;Fuzzybutz&#x27; grooming salon, where master groomers provide technical breed-specific styling and therapeutic hygiene treatments using only the finest non-toxic, all-natural products. The daycare experience here is uniquely designed to mirror a restorative home environment, replacing traditional kennels with a &#x27;living room&#x27; setting complete with designer furniture, cots, and entertainment systems that keep dogs calm and socially engaged in a peaceful, open-play layout.\n\nThe amenities at this premier Madison Street hub extend beyond the salon to include an expansive, secure backyard play area where dogs can transition between climate-controlled comfort and outdoor sunshine, often featuring interactive pool play and professional surround-sound audio to enhance the social atmosphere. For owners requiring more than just daycare, the facility offers a comprehensive &#x27;Professional Paws&#x27; menu that includes GPS-tracked walking sessions (available in 30 and 60-minute durations) and specialized in-home pet visits for medical oversight or food delivery. The facility also serves as a verified event space for high-end canine birthday parties, offering a secure and stylish backdrop for neighborhood pet celebrations. With its impressive 4.8-star rating and a verified history of responsive customer care, Urban Dog / Fuzzybutz delivers an authoritative and exceptionally helpful care solution for the Hoboken community. Whether your companion is in need of a technical deshedding treatment or a full day of open-play social proofing, the team here treats every guest with the elite logic and individualized heart the community has come to expect for over a decade.</p></div></a></div><div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:2rem\"><button class=\"hero-cta primary\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;cursor:pointer\"><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down\"></i>Show More (<!-- -->2<!-- --> more)</button></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!-- -->Hoboken</h2><p>Worth the drive? Check out top-rated indoor parks in neighboring cities.</p></div><div class=\"nearby-cities-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem\"><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/jersey-city\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in Jersey City, NJ\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/jersey-city/hero.webp\"/></div><div class=\"nearby-city-content\" style=\"padding:1rem\"><h3 style=\"font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:#0f172a\">Jersey City</h3><p style=\"font-size:0.875rem;color:#64748b\">47<!-- --> parks · <!-- -->4.5<!-- --> avg rating</p></div></a><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;borde